# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Build output is intentionally committed so the tool can be installed straight
# from GitHub's tarball URL without a build step (see README "Installation").
# Rebuild with `npm run build` and commit dist/ whenever src/ changes — CI fails
# if the committed dist/ is stale.

